abstract: >
  Pre-built Windows wheels for two Open3D-based GUI tools used in the TomatoPGT pipeline:
  CloudSeg for manual organ-level point-cloud annotation, and CloudGraph for semantic graph extraction
  and phenotype/trait export from annotated point clouds.

